<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>国土报最新头条</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 20:07:40 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>杀害耶路撒冷恐怖分子的以色列士兵开枪打伤平民</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldiers-who-killed-jerusalem-terrorists-shoot-and-wound-civilian/0000018c-216f-d9ef-abcd-3f6fb6a30000</link><description>在社交媒体上发布的耶路撒冷公交车站枪击事件的视频中，一名平民举起双手恳求以色列士兵不要开枪，随后他中弹倒地。</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 19:33:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/israeli-soldiers-who-killed-jerusalem-terrorists-shoot-and-wound-civilian/0000018c-216f-d9ef-abcd-3f6fb6a30000</guid></item><item><title>两名以色列妇女从哈马斯的囚禁中获释，另外八名妇女将在几小时后获释</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/two-israeli-women-freed-from-hamas-captivity-eight-more-set-to-be-released-hours-later/0000018c-2148-dc03-a9ec-3d7b21800000</link><description>据美国有线电视新闻网 (CNN) 报道，40 岁的阿米特·苏萨纳 (Amit Soussana) 和 21 岁的以色列-法国双重国籍的米亚·谢姆 (Mia Schem) 比其他人更早获释，因为人质被关押在加沙各地的不同地点。</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 18:13:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/two-israeli-women-freed-from-hamas-captivity-eight-more-set-to-be-released-hours-later/0000018c-2148-dc03-a9ec-3d7b21800000</guid></item><item><title>Ofir Tzarfati 于 10 月 7 日在 Nova 音乐节上被绑架，被发现死于加沙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/ofir-tzarfati-abducted-during-the-rave-was-found-dead-in-gaza/0000018c-210d-dc03-a9ec-3d7f5ac90000</link><description>以色列军队在加沙地带与哈马斯作战时发现了他的尸体，并将其归还给以色列。同样在周四，据信也被哈马斯囚禁的阿维夫·阿齐利 (Aviv Atzili) 的家人获悉他的死讯。他的伴侣利亚特于周三从哈马斯的囚禁中获释</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 17:50:46 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/ofir-tzarfati-abducted-during-the-rave-was-found-dead-in-gaza/0000018c-210d-dc03-a9ec-3d7f5ac90000</guid></item><item><title>为什么哈马斯杀手援引上帝的名字，而不是解放巴勒斯坦</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/why-hamas-killers-invoked-gods-name-not-the-liberation-of-palestine/0000018c-2136-d21c-abae-77be854e0000</link><description>如果有人想找到解决以色列-巴勒斯坦冲突的办法，接受这样一个事实：这首先是一场宗教民族主义冲突 — — 而不是从西方校园引进的某种基于种族和定居者殖民的人为概念 — — 将是一个绝佳的选择开始</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 17:38:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/why-hamas-killers-invoked-gods-name-not-the-liberation-of-palestine/0000018c-2136-d21c-abae-77be854e0000</guid></item><item><title>震惊世界的选举结果：反穆斯林极右翼如何在荷兰取得胜利</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-elections-that-shook-the-world-how-the-anti-muslim-far-right-won-the-netherlands/0000018c-2019-d9ef-abcd-3e3923060000</link><description>荷兰政治专家警告说，当中右翼政党寻求在极右翼问题上竞争时，他们只能成功地使极端分子合法化并为他们打开权力之门</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 17:33:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/world-news/europe/2023-11-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/the-elections-that-shook-the-world-how-the-anti-muslim-far-right-won-the-netherlands/0000018c-2019-d9ef-abcd-3e3923060000</guid></item><item><title>英雄与恶棍：为什么亨利·基辛格对犹太人和以色列人来说是一个如此矛盾的人物</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/hero-and-villain-why-henry-kissinger-was-such-an-ambivalent-figure-for-jews-and-israelis/0000018c-209b-dc03-a9ec-3cfb59cc0000</link><description>基辛格是一名来自纳粹德国的儿童难民，后来成为 20 世纪最有影响力的犹太人物之一。在对尼克松反犹太主义的绥靖和中东穿梭外交的发明之间，他作为美国人和犹太人都留下了有争议的遗产</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 16:30:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/us-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/hero-and-villain-why-henry-kissinger-was-such-an-ambivalent-figure-for-jews-and-israelis/0000018c-209b-dc03-a9ec-3cfb59cc0000</guid></item><item><title>国家预算传奇证明内塔尼亚胡并没有意识到他的政府已经注定失败</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/state-budget-approval-saga-proves-netanyahu-doesnt-get-that-his-government-is-doomed/0000018c-20aa-da36-a1de-67af6b3e0000</link><description>内塔尼亚胡在战时违背公众情绪，贿赂极端正统联盟伙伴来拯救政府，他依赖于他的主要竞争对手、战时内阁成员本尼·甘茨——他正在等待离开政府并开始行动的合适时机。驱逐他的过程</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 16:24:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/state-budget-approval-saga-proves-netanyahu-doesnt-get-that-his-government-is-doomed/0000018c-20aa-da36-a1de-67af6b3e0000</guid></item><item><title>阿拉伯裔以色列孕妇被刺死；警方逮捕两名家庭成员</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/pregnant-arab-israeli-woman-stabbed-to-death-police-arrest-two-family-members/0000018c-20cd-dc03-a9ec-3cffd7ac0000</link><description>正值妊娠末期的阿雅·阿布·哈贾吉 (Aya Abu Hajjaj) 被送往医院进行紧急剖腹产，试图挽救婴儿，但最终医护人员不得不宣布两人死亡。</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 16:18:39 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/pregnant-arab-israeli-woman-stabbed-to-death-police-arrest-two-family-members/0000018c-20cd-dc03-a9ec-3cffd7ac0000</guid></item><item><title>纳莱迪人真的埋葬了死者吗？现在有办法可以查到</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-11-30/ty-article-magazine/did-homo-naledi-really-bury-its-dead-now-there-are-ways-to-find-out/0000018c-2080-d9ef-abcd-3ea10b130000</link><description>一篇新论文提出了利用地球科学技术来减少考古发现的不确定性的案例，例如是否有小脑人类在墙壁上雕刻并埋葬了死者</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 16:02:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-11-30/ty-article-magazine/did-homo-naledi-really-bury-its-dead-now-there-are-ways-to-find-out/0000018c-2080-d9ef-abcd-3ea10b130000</guid></item><item><title>闭嘴跳舞：特拉维夫的俱乐部场景因不关心政治而付出代价</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/our-parties-contributed-to-the-deafening-whitewashing-of-the-state-of-israel/0000018c-15a0-dd03-a7ff-bfb85afb0000</link><description>自 2002 年“狂欢反对占领”以来，以色列的夜生活场景和政治活动之间就没有任何联系。现在我们在世界舞台上为此付出了沉重的代价</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 15:49:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/our-parties-contributed-to-the-deafening-whitewashing-of-the-state-of-israel/0000018c-15a0-dd03-a7ff-bfb85afb0000</guid></item><item><title>新研究揭穿了来自埃巴勒山的有争议的圣经“诅咒碑”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-11-30/ty-article/new-studies-debunk-controversial-biblical-curse-tablet-from-mt-ebal/0000018c-20b6-d21c-abae-76bee75f0000</link><description>在约旦河西岸的“约书亚祭坛”发现的一块铅碑被吹捧为最古老的希伯来铭文。怀疑论者怀疑它什么也没说，而是一个钓鱼重量</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 15:37:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/archaeology/2023-11-30/ty-article/new-studies-debunk-controversial-biblical-curse-tablet-from-mt-ebal/0000018c-20b6-d21c-abae-76bee75f0000</guid></item><item><title>谁来统治加沙？谁来重建它？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-30/ty-article-opinion/.premium/who-will-govern-gaza-who-will-rebuild-it/0000018c-2093-d9ef-abcd-3eb3726b0000</link><description>战后第二天，将出现安全、治理以及谁将为加沙真正大规模重建买单的根本问题 — — 这些努力对于防止导致 10 月 7 日的激进化至关重要</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 15:15:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-30/ty-article-opinion/.premium/who-will-govern-gaza-who-will-rebuild-it/0000018c-2093-d9ef-abcd-3eb3726b0000</guid></item><item><title>在与哈马斯作战时受伤：“身体上有所进步，但情感上的挑战变得更加困难”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/wounded-battling-hamas-you-progress-physically-but-the-emotional-challenge-gets-harder/0000018c-2038-d9ef-abcd-3e393e430000</link><description>特拉维夫附近一家医院的康复中心里挤满了 10 月 7 日拯救生命的以色列士兵。现在，他们决心康复，以纪念那些未能幸存的朋友</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 14:29:47 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/wounded-battling-hamas-you-progress-physically-but-the-emotional-challenge-gets-harder/0000018c-2038-d9ef-abcd-3e393e430000</guid></item><item><title>以色列必须澄清：不驱逐加沙人。加沙没有以色列定居点</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-30/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-must-clarify-no-expulsion-of-gazans-no-israeli-settlements-in-gaza/0000018c-2043-dc03-a9ec-3c7b97600000</link><description>我们，一群以色列哲学家，为以色列辩护，免遭战争罪指控。但我们震惊地听到内塔尼亚胡政府中要求使加沙人永久流离失所的险恶声音：这将是反人类罪</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 14:22:30 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-11-30/ty-article-opinion/.premium/israel-must-clarify-no-expulsion-of-gazans-no-israeli-settlements-in-gaza/0000018c-2043-dc03-a9ec-3c7b97600000</guid></item><item><title>不是两个国家，不是一个国家：以色列人和巴勒斯坦人摆脱灾难的新出路</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/not-two-states-not-one-state-a-new-way-out-of-disaster-for-israelis-and-palestinians/0000018c-1fc0-d21c-abae-7ffc7f960000</link><description>只要看看加沙就知道以色列和巴勒斯坦的艰难分离会带来什么。坚固的围栏、地下屏障——如果更多的开放和更少的隔离是更好的答案呢？听起来很疯狂，但有一个逻辑</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 14:20:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/not-two-states-not-one-state-a-new-way-out-of-disaster-for-israelis-and-palestinians/0000018c-1fc0-d21c-abae-7ffc7f960000</guid></item><item><title>一名拉比法庭法官、一名校长和一名怀孕教师：耶路撒冷恐怖袭击的以色列受害者身份已确定</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/israeli-victims-of-hamas-jerusalem-terror-attack-identified/0000018c-2032-d9ef-abcd-3e3352170000</link><description>周四上午耶路撒冷枪击事件的三名受害者被确认为 73 岁的拉比 Elimelech Wasserman、67 岁的 Hanna Ifergan 和 24 岁的 Liviya Dickman</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 13:54:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/israeli-victims-of-hamas-jerusalem-terror-attack-identified/0000018c-2032-d9ef-abcd-3e3352170000</guid></item><item><title>伦敦议会取消烛台安装，担心加沙战争“加剧紧张局势”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/london-council-calls-off-menorah-instillation-fearing-inflaming-tensions-amid-gaza-war/0000018c-1fb7-d9ef-abcd-1fb734aa0000</link><description>在一封泄露的电子邮件中，官员们表示，临时安装比每年在整个假期期间展示巨型烛台更合适。自持续冲突开始以来，英国的反犹太主义事件急剧增加</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 13:15:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/jewish/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/london-council-calls-off-menorah-instillation-fearing-inflaming-tensions-amid-gaza-war/0000018c-1fb7-d9ef-abcd-1fb734aa0000</guid></item><item><title>随着哈马斯人质协议的落实，以色列考虑允许释放人质的选择</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/as-hamas-hostage-deal-materializes-israel-considers-options-to-also-allow-mens-release/0000018c-202b-da36-a1de-672ff0e30000</link><description>周四的人质释放预计将把最后一批以色列妇女和儿童从加沙地带带回以色列。一位熟悉谈判的消息人士表示，“每个人都清楚，现在恢复战斗将大大减少在不久的将来达成进一步协议的机会”</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 13:14:28 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/as-hamas-hostage-deal-materializes-israel-considers-options-to-also-allow-mens-release/0000018c-202b-da36-a1de-672ff0e30000</guid></item><item><title>以色列-加沙战争进入新阶段：拯救大兵内塔尼亚胡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/how-do-you-gaslight-an-entire-nation-ask-netanyahu/0000018c-1f93-db78-adcc-bfffdcbf0000</link><description>不出所料，总理本杰明·内塔尼亚胡将竭尽全力避免为以色列历史上最严重的灾难承担责任，甚至对 10 月 7 日及其后果提出全新的叙述</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 12:43:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article/.premium/how-do-you-gaslight-an-entire-nation-ask-netanyahu/0000018c-1f93-db78-adcc-bfffdcbf0000</guid></item><item><title>针对以色列的秘密学术抵制：“美国机构不会有以色列研究人员”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/covert-academic-boycott-against-israel-u-s-institutions-wont-have-israeli-researchers/0000018c-1c07-d9ef-abcd-1e274e0f0000</link><description>当地教授表示，自针对哈马斯的战争开始以来，西方校园的反以色列情绪正在减缓与以色列研究人员的合作：“拒绝审查出版物，拒绝参加以色列的会议，并终止邀请”去国外参加会议&amp;#39;</description><pubDate>Thu, 30 Nov 2023 12:25:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-11-30/ty-article-magazine/.premium/covert-academic-boycott-against-israel-u-s-institutions-wont-have-israeli-researchers/0000018c-1c07-d9ef-abcd-1e274e0f0000</guid></item></channel></rss>